rect/4b33c45f-230f-47a3-b358-f263da52d1b6?r=3D9p0gt ] for sponsoring the ma=
gic!=20
That=E2=80=99s all for today. We=E2=80=99ll be back with Weekly Dose of Opt=
imism lucky number 13 on Friday. Have a great week!=20
Thanks for reading,=20
Packy

